content:
Halleluiah, Halleluiah, Offer Him sacrifices of praise;
carry clean gifts, and enter the courts of the Lord, and
worship the Lord, before His holy altar, Halleluiah.

Remember We
Those prophets and apostles
Who preached the Christ to Gentiles;
Those crowned ones just and righteous;
Those martyrs and confessors,
Who bore torments and distress;
Godís Mother, saintly heroes,
Those faithful departed ones;
Their entreaties be for us,
At all times a strong fortress.
